    "created_at": "2013-11-05T00:47:23Z",
    "updated_at": "2013-11-05T00:47:23Z",
    "author_association": "MEMBER",
    "body": "We decided that using a consistent location for config across platforms was more important than following the XDG recommendations. We want to be able to tell users where their config files are, without having to ask which platform they're on. Also, we were never actually using the XDG directories properly - we mixed config with application data that should go in .local, and probably some runtime files that should be in $XDG_RUNTIME_DIR.\n\nBrief minutes are at https://hackpad.com/IPython-dev-meetings-6wTSjJt7TZK , and you can watch the video to see the full discussion.\n"
  },
